---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Somatic Services | Mikey Somatics">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-sand">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm tracking-widest uppercase text-sage mb-3">Services</p>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-light text-forest mb-6">Somatic Trauma Packages</h1>
        <p class="text-charcoal/70 leading-relaxed">
          Together, we'll gently expand the edges of your comfort zone, helping you feel more balanced and able to navigate challenges without feeling overwhelmed or shutting down.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <img src="/images/services-hero.png" alt="Somatic therapy session" class="rounded-2xl shadow-lg w-full" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How Sessions Work -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <p class="text-sm tracking-widest uppercase text-sage mb-3 text-center">Somatic Work</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-light text-forest mb-10 text-center">What to Expect</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6 text-charcoal/70 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          We'll start our time together working with grounding, centering, and orienting practices to help you feel present and connected to your inner resources&mdash;anything that brings you a sense of safety, support, and stability.
        </p>
        <p>
          Throughout the work, we'll gently dip into the more intense sensations and emotions, allowing you to experience and release stuck energy and impulses.
        </p>
        <p>
          Through regular check-ins, we will reconnect you to your resources and re-establish a sense of security.
        </p>
        <p>
          As we close our time together, we'll take time to integrate what you've experienced, helping you absorb insights and reconnect with yourself.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-sand">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-light text-forest mb-16 text-center">Packages</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">

        <!-- Foundations -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow flex flex-col">
          <h3 class="text-forest font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Foundations Package</h3>
          <p class="text-3xl font-light text-forest mb-1">$895</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/50 mb-6">one time</p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-charcoal/70 mb-8 flex-1">
            <li>5 private 60-minute sessions ($179/session)</li>
            <li>Space to slow down, build awareness, and begin listening to what your body is holding.</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="block text-center bg-forest text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full text-sm hover:bg-forest-light transition-colors">
            Get Started
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Standard -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow border-2 border-forest flex flex-col">
          <h3 class="text-forest font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Standard Package</h3>
          <p class="text-3xl font-light text-forest mb-1">$1,360</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/50 mb-6">$680/mo for 2 months</p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-charcoal/70 mb-8 flex-1">
            <li>8 private 60-minute sessions ($170/session)</li>
            <li>More room to go deeper after building your foundation, with a personalized plan for mapping and shifting patterns between sessions.</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="block text-center bg-forest text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full text-sm hover:bg-forest-light transition-colors">
            Get Started
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Comprehensive -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow flex flex-col">
          <h3 class="text-forest font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Comprehensive Intensive</h3>
          <p class="text-3xl font-light text-forest mb-1">$1,980</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/50 mb-6">$990/mo for 2 months</p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-charcoal/70 mb-8 flex-1">
            <li>12 private 60-minute sessions ($165/session)</li>
            <li>Enough trust to go into harder material, work with the body more directly, and address layered patterns that shorter containers can't reach.</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="block text-center bg-forest text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full text-sm hover:bg-forest-light transition-colors">
            Get Started
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Single -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow flex flex-col">
          <h3 class="text-forest font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Single Session</h3>
          <p class="text-3xl font-light text-forest mb-1">$200</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/50 mb-6">one time</p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-charcoal/70 mb-8 flex-1">
            <li>1 private 60-minute somatic session</li>
            <li>Start with one session to experience the work and see if it feels right for you.</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="block text-center bg-forest text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full text-sm hover:bg-forest-light transition-colors">
            Get Started
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Practice -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <p class="text-sm tracking-widest uppercase text-sage mb-3">The Practice</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-light text-forest mb-8">Healing Is Possible</h2>
      <p class="text-charcoal/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Healing from past wounds can feel uncomfortable and at times challenging&mdash;it is not only possible but necessary. Choosing to deepen your connection with your body and explore your relationships with yourself and others is an act of courage, love, and will ultimately create space for greater compassion and resilience.
      </p>
      <p class="text-charcoal/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        You, as a whole individual on this earth, deserve to feel supported and safe while knowing there is absolutely nothing wrong with you.
      </p>
      <p class="text-charcoal/70 leading-relaxed">
        Whether we're working with complex trauma or daily stress, my role is to be your copilot&mdash;guiding you at a pace that feels comfortable while helping to reduce your symptoms and discomfort. It is my responsibility to invest in your well-being and ensure you feel supported throughout our time together.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
